<h2 id="org5fa7df8">Login instructions</h2>
<div class="outline-text-2" id="text-org5fa7df8">
<p>
-&#x2014; get a login &#x2014;  
</p>

<ul class="org-ul">
<li>Go toÂ [<a href="https://account.mcs.cmu.edu/">https://account.mcs.cmu.edu/</a>](<a href="https://account.mcs.cmu.edu/">https://account.mcs.cmu.edu/</a>)</li>
<li>Choose option 1</li>
<li>If prompted, enter your cmu andrewid and cmu password</li>
<li>type your desired cluster password twice (can be the same as andrew password or different) and tick "squadron" only</li>
<li>click submit and wait for confirmation of your request on the webpage</li>
</ul>
